aa(lp15
VWe call it, "There's a Better Way."
p16
aVWe call it There's a Better Way
p17
aVbecause I believe there's a better way to get the money you need
p18
aVthan panhandling on the corner.
p19
aVI believe there's a better way to help your brothers and sisters in need
p20
aVthan handing a few dollars out the car window.
p21
aVWe know there's dignity in work.
p22
aVWe also know that people are much more likely to invest in themselves
p23
aVif they believe that their community is willing to invest in them first.
p24
aVAnd because we're all wired to be kind and compassionate,
p25
aVit always feels good to hand a couple of dollars to someone
p26
aVthat is in need.
p27
aVBut if you talk to panhandlers, many of them will tell you
p28
aVthat your few dollars don't necessarily go towards feeding the body,
p29
aVthey go towards feeding an addiction.
p30
aVThere's a better way.
p31
aa(lp32
VMy name is Richard Berry,
p33
aVand I have one of the best jobs in the world.
p34
aVI get to be the mayor of a great American city,
p35
aVAlbuquerque, New Mexico.
p36
aVI was at lunch on July 17, 2015, in my great American city,
p37
aVand on my way back to city hall,
p38
aVI saw this gentleman standing on a corner.
p39
aVAs you can see, he's holding a sign,
p40
aVand his sign says he wants a job.
p41
aVBut if you look closer at the picture,
p42
aVyou'll see he's standing underneath a blue sign,
p43
aVand that sign says, if you need help, if you need food or shelter
p44
aVor you'd like to donate,
p45
aVplease call 311, our community service number.
p46
aa(lp47
VSo why is this guy standing underneath my sign with his sign?
p48
aVWell, we wondered if anybody would call that 311 sign,
p49
aVand as it turns out, they did \u2014
p50
aV11,000 times people called.
p51
aVI put those up in about 30 intersections.
p52
aVAnd we did connect them with food and shelter and services.
p53
aVBut yet he's still standing under my sign
p54
aVwith a sign that says he wants a job.
p55
aVIt's simple: he wants a job.
p56
aVSo I decided to do something rare in government.
p57
aVI decided to make the solution simpler rather than more complicated.
p58
aVI went back to my office, I gathered my staff around
p59
aVand I said, "We're going to take this man at his word,
p60
aVand others like him.
p61
aVThe man says he wants a job, we're going to give him a job,
p62
aVand we're going to make our city an even better place in the meantime."
