aa(lp64
VYou see, Albuquerque is a beautiful place.
p65
aVWe're a mile high,
p66
aVthe Sandia Mountains on the east,
p67
aVthe Rio Grande runs through the center of the city;
p68
aVwe're the home of the Albuquerque International Balloon Fiesta.
