aVOn a day like today,
p70
aVyou could literally ski this morning and golf this afternoon.
p71
aVBut there's always something to do \u2014
p72
aValways weeds to pull, litter to pick up.
p73
aVIf you're going to have an initiative like this in your city,
p74
aVyou have to ask yourself two questions.
p75
aVFirst one is: Is there anything left to do in your city?
p76
aVAnd if the answer is no,
p77
aVwould you please give me your mayor's phone number,
p78
aVbecause I need some advice.
p79
aa(lp80
V(Laughter)
