aa(lp82
VBut the second question you have to ask is this:
p83
aVAre your solutions to panhandling working?
p84
aVIf you're like Albuquerque,
p85
aVand you're taking the punitive approach like we used to,
p86
aVhanding out tickets to panhandlers or those who give them money,
p87
aVI'm going to suggest that your solutions aren't working,
p88
aVand I know you're not getting to the root of your problem in your city.
p89
aVSo if you have something to do
p90
aVand you need people that need something to do,
p91
aVthere's a better way.
p92
aVAnd the good news is, it's not that complicated.
