aa(lp94
VThis a 2006 Dodge van.
p95
aVIt was in my motor pool not doing anything.
p96
aVWe put some new tires on it, wrapped it with a logo.
p97
aVThis van now goes out to street corners where our panhandlers are \u2014
p98
aVwe go to them.
p99
aVWe stop the van, we get out,
p100
aVwe ask them if they would like a day's work
p101
aVrather than panhandling for the day.
p102
aVAnd if you wondered if they really mean it \u2014
p103
aVit takes us about an hour to fill this van up in the morning,
p104
aVbecause almost everybody we ask takes a job for the day.
